  "description": "A breathtaking view of a sunset over calm water, featuring a distant bridge and silhouetted landforms. The sky is ablaze with warm colors, transitioning from vibrant orange and yellow near the horizon to deep shades of purple and grey higher up. The water reflects the colors of the sky, creating a sense of serenity and vastness. A bridge with distinct towers spans the water, partially obscured by the distance. Dark, rolling hills or mountains are visible in the background, adding depth to the landscape. A small structure is faintly visible in the water near the bridge.",
